description: The video shows a cartoon woman with blond wavy hair and blue eyes. She is wearing a light blue sailor-style top with white stripes on the collar and sleeves, and a matching blue hat. Her skin tone is light, and she has red lipstick on. She is looking slightly to the right. The word "Hush" appears in a reddish-orange color next to her. Then, she puts her finger to her lips as if telling someone to be quiet, while still looking to the right. The word "Hush" reappears.
